nodes.title: README
widgets_values:
# **Using Controlnet**

# - My suggestion is to enable Controlnet only in stage 1 and 2. It is so damn slow
# - If you want to use controlnet:

# 1. If you want to use it with a LoRA, you can use "Model with LoRA" for stage 1 and "Model with LoRA and EasyCache 2nd Stage" for stage 2 in get model inside the controlnet group

# 2. If you want to use it without a LoRA, you can use "Model with LoRA" for both stage 1 and stage 2 in get model inside the controlnet group
